requestedAttributes.onlySatisfiedDescrip.translation: Kartat e mëposhtme do të ndahen.

signShare.documentIntro.message: The following document will be signed.
comments: Text above the document to be signed
signShare.documentIntro.translation: Dokumenti i mëposhtëm do të nënshkruhet.

presentationNotification.infoWillBePrese.message: The following information will be presented:
comments: Text shown before listing information that will be presented in response to an information request
presentationNotification.infoWillBePrese.translation: Informacioni i mëposhtëm do të paraqitet:

signShare.cardIntro.message: The following personal information will be used to sign the document.
comments: Explains which info will be used to sign
signShare.cardIntro.translation: Informacioni personal i mëposhtëm do të përdoret për të nënshkruar dokumentin.

cardLifecycle.revoked.sheetDescription.message: The issuer has revoked this card and it can not be used anymore. Contact the issuer for more information.
cardLifecycle.revoked.sheetDescription.translation: Lëshuesi e ka anuluar këtë kartë dhe nuk mund të përdoret më. Kontakto lëshuesin për më shumë informacion.

comments: Label shown above optional extra description

requestPurpose.overaskingWarning.message: The purpose given does not match the data requested.
comments: Warning shown when the declared purpose does not align with the data requested by the organization
requestPurpose.overaskingWarning.translation: Qëllimi i dhënë nuk përputhet me të dhënat e kërkuara.

cardLifecycle.limitedByDate.validityPeri.message: The validity period of this card is from {0} until {1}.
cardLifecycle.limitedByDate.validityPeri.translation: Periudha e vlefshmërisë së kësaj karte është nga {0} deri më {1}.

trust.noApprovals.message: There are no organizations that have approved {name}.
comments: A message shown when there are no organizations that approved the current party
trust.noApprovals.translation: Nuk ka organizata që kanë aprovuar {name}.

trust.noApprovalsWithoutOrganizationName.message: There are no organizations that have approved this unknown organization.
comments: A message shown when there are no organizations that approved the current party, but the organization name is not known
trust.noApprovalsWithoutOrganizationName.translation: Nuk ka organizata që kanë aprovuar këtë organizatë të panjohur.

comments: Shown when the user has no credentials
Shown when the user has no activity items yet

onboardingIdCardRequestedAttributes.desc.message: These {0} attributes will be read from your eID card.
comments: Text explaining how many attributes will be read from the eID card
onboardingIdCardRequestedAttributes.desc.translation: Këto {0} atribute do të lexohen nga karta jote eID.

confirmationSheet.description.translation: Ky veprim nuk mund të zhbëhet.

qrScanner.permissionDescription.message: This allows the app to scan QR codes that include credentials or data requests.
comments: Description explaining why camera permission is needed
qrScanner.permissionDescription.translation: Kjo lejon aplikacionin të skanojë kode QR që përmbajnë kredenciale ose kërkesa të dhënash.

offlineQr.allowBluetoothAccessDescriptio.message: This allows the app to share with a QR code.
offlineQr.allowBluetoothAccessDescriptio.translation: Kjo lejon aplikacionin të ndajë me kod QR.

paradymWallet.about.description.message: This app was created by Animo Solutions as a companion app for Paradym. All code is available under Apache 2.0.
comments: About screen description text for the Paradym wallet
paradymWallet.about.description.translation: Ky aplikacion u krijua nga Animo Solutions si një aplikacion shoqërues për Paradym. I gjithë kodi është i disponueshëm nën Apache 2.0.

funkeWallet.about.description.message: This app was created by Animo Solutions in the context of the SPRIN-D Funke ‘EUDI Wallet Prototypes’. It serves as a prototype for future wallet providers. All code is available under Apache 2.0.
comments: About screen description text for the Funke wallet
funkeWallet.about.description.translation: Ky aplikacion u krijua nga Animo Solutions në kontekstin e SPRIN-D Funke 'EUDI Wallet Prototypes'. Shërben si një prototip për ofruesit e ardhshëm të portofolit. I gjithë kodi është i disponueshëm nën Apache 2.0.

cardLifecycle.batch.sheetDescription.message: This card requires periodic validation using an internet connection. When usage is low you will be notified.
cardLifecycle.batch.sheetDescription.translation: Kjo kartë kërkon vërtetim periodik duke përdorur lidhjen e internetit. Kur përdorimi është i ulët, do të njoftohesh.

cardLifecycle.limitedByDate.activeIn.message: This card will be active in {activeDaysString}, on {0}.
cardLifecycle.limitedByDate.activeIn.translation: Kjo kartë do të jetë aktive në {activeDaysString}, më {0}.

presentationNotification.missingCredenti.message: This credential is not present in your wallet.
comments: Shown when a required credential is missing
presentationNotification.missingCredenti.translation: Ky kredencial nuk është i pranishëm në portofolin tënd.

localAi.toast.unsupported.message.message: This device is not powerful enough to run local AI models
comments: Message shown when device cannot handle the AI model
localAi.toast.unsupported.message.translation: Kjo pajisje nuk është mjaft e fuqishme për të drejtuar modele AI lokale

common.featureNotSupported.message: This feature is not supported in this version of the app.
comments: Shown when a feature that is not supported is accessed
common.featureNotSupported.translation: Kjo veçori nuk mbështetet në këtë version të aplikacionit.

localAi.confirm.description2.message: This is an experimental feature. Only supported on high-end devices.
comments: Second paragraph of confirmation sheet warning about device compatibility
localAi.confirm.description2.translation: Kjo është një veçori eksperimentale. Mbështetet vetëm në pajisje të klasit të lartë.

comments: Title shown for offline message

pidSetup.idCardPin.subtitle.message: This is required to read data from your card.
pidSetup.idCardPin.subtitle.translation: Kjo kërkohet për të lexuar të dhëna nga karta jote.

onboardingWelcome.description.message: This is your digital wallet. With it, you can store and share information about yourself.
comments: Intro paragraph on the welcome screen
onboardingWelcome.description.translation: Ky është portofoli yt dixhital. Me të, mund të ruash dhe ndash informacion rreth vetes.

comments: Title for first slide of wallet onboarding
Heading shown on empty wallet screen

requestPurpose.infoSheet.description.message: This organization seems to be asking for different or more data than their purpose suggests. Read the request carefully. You can deny the request if you do not agree with the data asked.
comments: Description text in the overasking info sheet
requestPurpose.infoSheet.description.translation: Kjo organizatë duket se po kërkon të dhëna të ndryshme ose më shumë se sa tregon qëllimi i tyre. Lexoje kërkesën me kujdes. Mund ta refuzosh kërkesën nëse nuk pajtohesh me të dhënat e kërkuara.

onboarding.pin.subtitle.message: This PIN secures your identity wallet. You enter it every time you share data.
comments: Explanation of the PIN purpose in onboarding
onboarding.pin.subtitle.translation: Ky PIN siguron portofolin tënd të identitetit. E fut çdo herë që ndan të dhëna.

localAi.confirm.description1.message: This will download a local AI model to your device which will take up to around 1.3GB of space.
comments: First paragraph of confirmation sheet explaining model size
localAi.confirm.description1.translation: Kjo do të shkarkojë një model AI lokal në pajisjen tënde që do të zërë rreth 1.3GB hapësirë.

common.archiveCardDescription.message: This will make {name} unusable and delete it from your wallet.
comments: Description in confirmation dialog explaining card archiving
common.archiveCardDescription.translation: Kjo do ta bëjë {name} të papërdorshme dhe do ta fshijë nga portofoli yt.

pidSetup.enableBiometrics.subtitle.message: To continue, make sure your device has biometric protection enabled, and that Paradym Wallet is allowed to use biometrics.
pidSetup.enableBiometrics.subtitle.translation: Për të vazhduar, sigurohu që pajisja jote ka aktivizuar mbrojtjen biometrike, dhe që Paradym Wallet lejohet të përdorë biometrikë.

credentialCardSlide.subtitle.pin.message: To receive this card from {issuerName}, you need to enter a PIN.
comments: Subtitle shown when entering a PIN is required to receive the credential
credentialCardSlide.subtitle.pin.translation: Për të marrë këtë kartë nga {issuerName}, duhet të futësh një PIN.

credentialCardSlide.subtitle.presentatio.message: To receive this card from {issuerName}, you need to share cards from your wallet.
comments: Subtitle shown when presentation of other credentials is required
credentialCardSlide.subtitle.presentatio.translation: Për të marrë këtë kartë nga {issuerName}, duhet të ndash karta nga portofoli yt.

txCodeSlide.instructions.message: To receive this card you need to enter a transaction code. This code has been provided to you by the issuer.
comments: Instructions explaining why the user must enter a transaction code
txCodeSlide.instructions.translation: Për të marrë këtë kartë duhet të futësh një kod transaksioni. Ky kod të është dhënë nga lëshuesi.

authCodeFlowSlide.description.message: To receive this card, you need to authorize with your account. You will now be redirected to the issuer's website.
comments: Explanation for why user is redirected to external site
authCodeFlowSlide.description.translation: Për të marrë këtë kartë, duhet të autorizosh me llogarinë tënde. Tani do të ridrejtohesh te faqja e internetit e lëshuesit.

qrScanner.instructionHeading.message: Use the camera to scan a QR code

qrScanner.instructionHeading.translation: Përdor kamerën për të skanuar një kod QR

pinSlide.description.message: Use your app PIN code to confirm the request.
comments: Supporting text explaining why PIN is needed
pinSlide.description.translation: Përdor kodin PIN të aplikacionit për të konfirmuar kërkesën.

menu.setupEid.message.message: Use your eID card to set up your digital identity.
comments: Explanation for setting up eID card
menu.setupEid.message.translation: Përdor kartën eID për të konfiguruar identitetin tënd dixhital.

onboardingIntroduction.step2.description.message: Use your ID card PIN to retrieve your identity information.
comments: Description of the second onboarding step about reading identity info
onboardingIntroduction.step2.description.translation: Përdor PIN-in e kartës së identitetit për të marrë informacionin e identitetit tënd.

pidSetup.idCardVerify.Subtitle.message: We need your biometrics to verify your identity.
pidSetup.idCardVerify.Subtitle.translation: Na nevojitet biometrika jote për të vërtetuar identitetin tënd.

comments: Welcome title in wallet screen
welcome.titleToYourWallet.translation: Mirë se erdhe në portofolin tënd

Title of toast when no internet or WiFi is available

<0>{name}</0>

nfcScanner.complete.description.message: You can now remove your eID card.
comments: Description when NFC scan completed successfully
nfcScanner.complete.description.translation: Tani mund ta heqësh kartën eID.

presentationSuccess.returnHint.message: You can now return to the previous app.
comments: Instruction shown after presentation is completed
presentationSuccess.returnHint.translation: Tani mund të kthehesh te aplikacioni i mëparshëm.

sharing.failed.missingCredentials.message: You did not have the required credentials to disclose.
comments: Displayed when the user tries to share but lacks the needed credentials
sharing.failed.missingCredentials.translation: Nuk i ke kredencialet e nevojshme për të zbuluar.

requestedAttributes.partialDescription.message: You don't have all of the requested cards.
comments: Description when the user has some but not all requested cards
requestedAttributes.partialDescription.translation: Nuk i ke të gjitha kartat e kërkuara.

inbox.emptyMessage.message: You don't have any notifications at the moment.
comments: Paragraph shown when the inbox is empty

noContentInbox.message.message: You don't have any notifications at the moment.
comments: Message shown when user has no notifications

requestedAttributes.onlyUnsatisfiedDescr.message: You don't have the requested card(s).
comments: Description when the user has none of the requested cards
requestedAttributes.onlyUnsatisfiedDescr.translation: Nuk i ke kartën/kartat e kërkuara.

signShare.missingCards.message: You don't have the required cards
comments: Shown when the user lacks the required credentials
signShare.missingCards.translation: Nuk i ke kartat e nevojshme

submission.missingCardsWarning.message: You don't have the required cards
comments: Shown when user lacks required credentials
submission.missingCardsWarning.translation: Nuk i ke kartat e nevojshme

presentationNotification.missingRequired.message: You don't have the required credentials to satisfy this request.
comments: Shown when the user lacks the required credentials to satisfy an information request
presentationNotification.missingRequired.translation: Nuk i ke kredencialet e nevojshme për të përmbushur këtë kërkesë.

pinLocked.description.message: You have entered an incorrect PIN. The wallet was locked, please reset it to set a new PIN and continue.
comments: Descriptive text explaining that the wallet is locked and must be reset
pinLocked.description.translation: Ke futur një PIN të gabuar. Portofoli u bllokua, rivendose për të vendosur një PIN të ri dhe vazhduar.

comments: Heading shown when user receives a credential when issuer name is not available

presentationNotification.receivedRequest.message: You have received an information request
comments: Heading shown when the user receives an information request without the verifier's name

presentationNotification.receivedRequest.message: You have received an information request from {verifierName}
comments: Heading shown when the user receives an information request including the verifier's name
presentationNotification.receivedRequest.translation: Ke marrë një kërkesë informacioni nga {verifierName}

activity.receivedSingle.message: You have received the following card from {0}.
comments: Shown in activity detail when one credential has been received
activity.receivedSingle.translation: Ke marrë kartën e mëposhtme nga {0}.

activity.receivedMultiple.message: You have received the following cards from {0}.
comments: Shown in activity detail when multiple credentials have been received
activity.receivedMultiple.translation: Ke marrë kartat e mëposhtme nga {0}.

onboardingIntroduction.reminder.message: You'll need your eID card to setup the wallet
comments: Reminder shown before user continues onboarding
onboardingIntroduction.reminder.translation: Do të të duhet karta eID për të konfiguruar portofolin

comments: Heading shown when the inbox is empty
Heading shown when user has no notifications

cardLifecycle.active.sheetDescription.message: Your credentials may expire or require an active internet connection to validate.
cardLifecycle.active.sheetDescription.translation: Kredencialet e tua mund të skadojnë ose kërkojnë një lidhje interneti aktive për t'u vërtetuar.

pidSetup.dataProtection.subtitle.message: Your data is secured with a PIN and biometrics. Each time you share data, we confirm your identity.
pidSetup.dataProtection.subtitle.translation: Të dhënat e tua janë të siguruara me PIN dhe biometrikë. Çdo herë që ndan të dhëna, konfirmojmë identitetin tënd.

pidSetup.idCardComplete.subtitle.message: Your information has been retrieved from your eID card.
pidSetup.idCardComplete.subtitle.translation: Informacioni yt është marrë nga karta jote eID.

comments: Shown after credentials are shared with a specific verifier
Shown after credentials are shared (no verifier name)

authenticate.pinRequiredToast.message: Your PIN is required to unlock the app
authenticate.pinRequiredToast.translation: PIN-i yt kërkohet për të hapur aplikacionin
